Class Description
admin
admin class is a child class which consist of data related to admin

This is the admin login GUI.
answers
Answer class store the data related to system which collect from the user
chartanalytics
chartanalytics class stores the data which will display in the charts it has implemented serializable because to store data into an object stream that we can send over the network or save it as file or store in database.
charts
This GUI display the chart image which is generated by the quickchart.io web service.
db_connection
Implementation of the remote interface.
homescreen
This is the home screen of the feedback system.
player
Stores the data related to player This the parent class of the admin class because both admin class and player class has set of similar variables It has implemented serializable because to store data into an object stream that we can send over the network or save it as file or store in database.
questionnaire
This class has the data related to questions.
questionnaireform
This GUI display the questions of the system and it allow user to submit the answers to the system.
questionscontroller
This class is accessible for all GUI's.

RMI interface which consist with abstract methods for various functionalities with database to exchange the data with server
rmi
RMI server implementation
